Title: An alternative formulation of classical electromagnetic duality

Authors: Kang Li, Carlos M. Na\'on

Comments: 14 pages, no figures, Latex, minor corrections, references and

acknowledgements addedJournal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A16 (2001) 1671-1684

By introducing a doublet of electromagnetic four dimensional vectorpotentials, we set up a manifestly Lorentz covariant and SO(2) dualityinvariant classical field theory of electric and magnetic charges. In ourformulation one does not need to introduce the concept of Dirac string.